</div>
</section></header>

  <div class="maincontentbettyland"><br><br>
<div class="editaccounttitle"><h1> Edit Account</h1><p>We know, there's a lot going on here.<br>This is your private, and public home here in Bettyland so grab some tea and take your time in filling out your profile.<br>And if you change your mind? You can always come back to redecorate.</p></div>
<section class="editaccountpage">
  <div class="maininfo loginform">
  <%= simple_form_for @user do |f| %>
  <section class="images">
    <div class="imagesphoto">
  <%= image_tag @user.photo.medium.url %><br><p>Upload a Bio Photo</p><br><%= f.input :photo, label: '📷', :input_html => { :class => 'photoinput' } %></div>
  <div class="imagesphoto">
    <%= image_tag @user.photogif.medium.url %><br><p>Upload a Boomerang of You</p><br><%= f.input :photogif, label: '📹', :input_html => { :class => 'photoinput' } %></div>
</section>
<div class="basicinfo">
  <%= f.input :ig_username %>
  <%= f.input :password, label: 'Change your Password' %>
  <%= f.input :password_confirmation %>
  <%= f.input :personalIG_link, label: 'Full Link to your IG profile' %>
  <%= f.input :spotify_profile, label: 'Are you on Spotify? Link your profile here.' %>

<h2> Tell us about you!</h2>
<p>What do you do? What are you into? Share anything you like here, but like, no pressure. Feel free to write as much or as little as you would like.</p>
  <%= f.input :about, label: '📝', :input_html => { :class => 'paragraph' } %>
</div>

<div class="comfortcorner userprofilesection">
  <h3>(JUST FOR YOU) Leave some gentle reminders for yourself here.</h3>
  <%= f.input :MHSroutine_1,  label: '1.' %>
  <%= f.input :MHSroutine_2,  label: '2.' %>
  <%= f.input :MHSroutine_3,  label: '3.' %>
</div>


</div>

<div class="maininfo loginform">
  <h2>Mental Health Shelf</h2>
  <p>This is where you can share what helps you take care of yourself with the Betty community.
  <br>Your Mental Health Shelfie is a snapshot of you- somewhere to remind you of the tools you already have, and a way for others to connect with you.
  Fill in as much or as little as you like. <br><br>Who knows,
  you may just find your next bestie, or at the very least, be inspiring, and inspired.</p>

  <div class="userprofilesection"><h3>Got any favourite quotes?</h3>
  <%= f.input :MHSquote_1,  label: '1.', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %>
  <%= f.input :MHSquote_2,  label: '2.', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %>
  <%= f.input :MHSquote_3,  label: '3.', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %></div>

    <div class="userprofilesection"><h3>What books or reads would you recommend?</h3>
  <%= f.input :MHSbook_1,  label: '1.', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %>
  <%= f.input :MHSbook_2,  label: '2.', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %>
  <%= f.input :MHSbook_3,  label: '3.', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %>
  <%= f.input :MHSbook_4,  label: '4.', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %>
  <%= f.input :MHSbook_5,  label: '5.', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %></div>

    <div class="userprofilesection"><h3>Any videos, resources, other links you would recommend?</h3>
  <%= f.input :MHSgeneral_1,  label: '1', placeholder: "Title", :input_html => { :class => 'mediuminput' } %><%= f.input :video_links1,  label: '🔗',  placeholder: 'Full link please!', :input_html => { :class => 'secondaryinput' } %><br>
  <%= f.input :MHSgeneral_3,  label: '2', placeholder: "Title", :input_html => { :class => 'mediuminput' } %><%= f.input :vide_links2,  label: '🔗.',  placeholder: 'Full link please!', :input_html => { :class => 'secondaryinput' } %><br>
  <%= f.input :MHSgeneral_4,  label: '3', placeholder: "Title", :input_html => { :class => 'mediuminput' } %><%= f.input :vide_links3,  label: '🔗.',  placeholder: 'Full link please!', :input_html => { :class => 'secondaryinput' } %><br>
  <%= f.input :MHSgeneral_5,  label: '4', placeholder: "Title", :input_html => { :class => 'mediuminput' } %><%= f.input :vide_links4,  label: '🔗.',  placeholder: 'Full link please!', :input_html => { :class => 'secondaryinput' } %><br>
  </div>

    <div class="userprofilesection"><h3>What are some of your favourite IG accounts?</h3>
  <%= f.input :MHSIG_1,  label: '1', placeholder: "Username", :input_html => { :class => 'smallerinput' } %> <%= f.input :IG_link1,  label: '🔗',  placeholder: 'Full link please!', :input_html => { :class => 'secondaryinput' } %><br>
  <%= f.input :MHSIG_2,  label: '2', placeholder: "Username", :input_html => { :class => 'smallerinput' } %> <%= f.input :IG_link2,  label: '🔗',  placeholder: 'Full link please!', :input_html => { :class => 'secondaryinput' } %><br>
  <%= f.input :MHSIG_3,  label: '3', placeholder: "Username", :input_html => { :class => 'smallerinput' } %><%= f.input :IG_link3,  label: '🔗',  placeholder: 'Full link please!', :input_html => { :class => 'secondaryinput' } %><br>
  <%= f.input :MHSIG_4,  label: '4', placeholder: "Username", :input_html => { :class => 'smallerinput' } %> <%= f.input :IG_link4,  label: '🔗',  placeholder: 'Full link please!', :input_html => { :class => 'secondaryinput' } %><br>
  <%= f.input :MHSIG_5,  label: '5', placeholder: "Username", :input_html => { :class => 'smallerinput' } %> <%= f.input :IG_link5,  label: '🔗',  placeholder: 'Full link please!', :input_html => { :class => 'secondaryinput' } %>
  </div>

    <div class="userprofilesection"><h3>Sure, you can't buy self-care, but what are some products that help?</h3>
  <%= f.input :MHSproduct_1,  label: '1', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %>
  <%= f.input :MHSroduct_2,  label: '2', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %>
  <%= f.input :MHSproduct_3,  label: '3', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %>
  <%= f.input :MHSproduct_4,  label: '4', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %>
  <%= f.input :MHSproduct_5,  label: '5', :input_html => { :class => 'MHSinput' } %>
  </div>

    <%= f.button :submit, "Update User Details" %>
  <% end %>

<h3>
  <%= link_to "Update Your Credit Card Details", edit_account_path %></h3><p>Need to delete your account? Let us know at hello@inbedwithbetty.com</p>
